sequentialGradientInterceptEstimator() - Method in class datascilib.Regression.LinearRegression.regression.LinearRegression
Calculates the LinearRegression.slope using sequential gradient descent with an initial intercept value of LinearRegression.INITIAL_INTERCEPT
sequentialSlopeEstimator() - Method in class datascilib.Regression.LinearRegression.regression.LinearRegression
Calculates the LinearRegression.slope sequentially using Least Mean Squared (LMS)

numerator = sum( (LinearRegression.x[index] - LinearRegression.xMean) * (LinearRegression.y[index] - LinearRegression.yMean))
denominator = sum( (LinearRegression.x[index] - LinearRegression.xMean)^2 )
LinearRegression.slope = numerator / denominator
sequentialSquareResidualSum(double) - Method in class datascilib.Regression.LinearRegression.regression.LinearRegression
Calculates the derivative sum squared residuals sequentially
